content:
Create a Work Plan Template

Simplify work plans for your incident management agents with work plan templates. Available in Lightning Experience with your standard Service Cloud license and in Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

To create:
- Create and Read on work plan templates
- Create and Read on work step templates

From the App Launcher, find and select Work Plan Templates.
Click New.
Enter a name, set the template to Active, and save your changes.
Add a list of work steps by adding the Work Steps related list to the Work Plan Template.

To associate existing work steps with your work plan template:
- Click Manage
- Add

Create a work step template by clicking New, then New Work Plan Step Template. 
Rearrange work step templates by clicking Manage, then Reorder.

After creating work plan templates and work step templates, agents can generate a work plan from the change request with out of the box steps.
title: Service Cloud Work Plan Template Setup
